OperettaManager - Class in ch.epfl.biop.operetta
Operetta Manager class This class handles all the Operetta logic to extract data The entry point is to call the OperettaManager.Builder class to create the correct OperettaManager object
OperettaManager.Builder - Class in ch.epfl.biop.operetta
This Builder class handles creating OperettaManager objects for you If you're curious about the Builder Pattern, you can read Joshua Bloch's excellent Effective Java Book Use When creating a new OperettaManager object, call the Builder, add all the options and then call the OperettaManager.Builder.build() method
